snippet.title: Kyn Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/314560/

Watch the new game trailer for the upcoming action-RPG, Kyn. Get a taste of the challenges that you can expect to face in this Viking-themed adventure game as you unravel an unexpected story that will keep you guessing until the very end.
